skunkmenu
=========
skunkmenu is dmenu interface for `skunk` a boring password manager.
it provide quick way to copy a password into the clipboard, without
having to open up a terminal window. 

Recommendation
--------------
Enable a shortcut, `Alt+S`, to launch skunkmenu while applying dwm 
patch [1], and applying dmenu patch [0] to hide typing.

Installation
------------
  
    go install github.com/n4x2/skunkmenu@latest

patch
-----
[0] https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/patches/password/
[1] https://gist.github.com/n4x2/5d89b7bf494eef8f9bc46ef431a912d2
